{"tid":467309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［昂山邪姬］UN揭緬甸軍有系統地輪姦羅興亞婦女","createTime":"2017-11-13T11:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T11:38:52.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70ed8924b69a7ff09617ed7273d62806b92f56f5","tid":467309,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"緬甸的羅興亞族進一步面臨人道危機。聯合國安理會關注性暴力特使帕頓 (Pramila Patten) 近日痛批緬甸政府軍涉嫌「有系統」地輪姦羅興亞婦女，甚至逼使她們成為性奴，直斥有關暴行嚴重違反人道原則，又指緬甸政府在背後策劃和執行，導致逃亡人潮加劇，甚至有人因此而喪命。<br />\n<br />\n外地傳媒報道，帕頓日前探訪逃離至孟加拉南部地區的羅興亞人，並聽聞不少令人震驚的強暴和輪暴故事，不少婦女曾經驚歷這些暴行，甚至有不少婦女喪命。<br />\n<br />\n帕頓表示，因為主族和信仰的關係，緬甸政府軍「有系統地鎖定」羅興亞女性為輪暴對象，發生在緬甸北部若開邦 (Rakhine) 的性暴力是受到緬甸武裝部隊指揮、策劃和執行。此外，她提到不少羅興亞婦女成為軍方性奴，其中有一名倖存者被緬甸軍方囚禁了45天，期間反覆遭到強暴，也有不少人被迫在公開場合裸體等。<br />\n<br />\n帕頓指出，目前聯合國已為1644名倖存者提供救援，但這數字只是冰山一角，由於孟加拉政府負擔太重，現在聯合國需要約1000萬美元的國際援助。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1064076/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1064076%2F&d=Wqqs1%2FQuREATe5Sljs4VV6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=c8a0b041\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1064076%2F&h=a14df78e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1064076/</a><br />\n仲話係和平獎得主<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/193349_5d7787853b92a4e4456bb71957f97ee7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F193349_5d7787853b92a4e4456bb71957f97ee7.jpg&h=58cd4e5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b84b76b22128d824409645930b99f69e8087844","tid":467309,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"證據呢"},{"pid":"831bd00249c086c08770e108d4094ee89e027377","tid":467309,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/193504_690d1a2fb24360e36c964666b44b1f7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F193504_690d1a2fb24360e36c964666b44b1f7e.jpg&h=5dd003b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb5bb89888a28c81947471429e2f0bfd524cc5e5","tid":467309,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"唔食豬肉的都是恐怖份子，殺無赦"},{"pid":"3dbd5c64545e5a7e887b9a23bf19755f67bbf870","tid":467309,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"361b1467fa135b528acffdaf01b354e7b46e9d4f","tid":467309,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"班穆斯林冇一個係無辜的"}]}